### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
### FinanceHQ – Transactions flow: manual Phase 2 checks
###   2.3 Create ONE_OFF EXPENSE (HOUSING) → 201
###   2.4 GET list → entry present
###   2.5 Create RECURRING INCOME → 201, nextExpectedDate computed
###       PATCH amount → 200
###       PATCH wrong user → 404
###       DELETE → 204; GET confirms gone
###       Create with wrong category for type → 400
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Prerequisites:
###   1. Server running on localhost:8080
###   2. Select "dev" environment (top-right in IntelliJ HTTP Client)
###   3. Run auth-flow.http Steps 1–2 first to populate accessToken
###   4. Run requests IN ORDER



### ─── 2.3: POST ONE_OFF EXPENSE — expect 201, category=HOUSING, nextExpectedDate=null ─
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "EXPENSE",
  "category": "HOUSING",
  "amount": 500.00,
  "description": "Monthly rent",
  "date": "2026-06-09"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("transactionId", response.body.id);
%}


### ─── 2.4: GET list — expect 200, list contains the created entry ─
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ─── 2.5: POST RECURRING INCOME — expect 201, nextExpectedDate computed, date=null ─
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "INCOME",
  "category": "SALARY",
  "amount": 5000.00,
  "period": "RECURRING",
  "paymentDay": 25
}

> {%
  client.global.set("recurringTransactionId", response.body.id);
%}


### ─── PATCH amount — expect 200, amount updated to 750.00 ───
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 750.00,
  "description": "Updated rent"
}


### ─── DELETE — expect 204 ───────────────────────────────────
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/{{recurringTransactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ─── GET after delete — expect 200, recurring entry gone ──
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ─── POST wrong category for type — expect 400 ────────────
### SALARY is an income category; using it with EXPENSE should return 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "EXPENSE",
  "category": "SALARY",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "date": "2026-06-09"
}


### ─── PATCH all-null body — expect 400 ──────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}


### ─── POST FIXED_TERM missing endDate — expect 400 ─────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "EXPENSE",
  "category": "FOOD",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "period": "FIXED_TERM",
  "paymentDay": 10,
  "remainingPayments": 6
}
